      <title>TPG 直接贷款部门为其第五只基金募集 39 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/tpg-direct-lending-unit-amasses-3-9-billion-for-its-fifth-fund</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，TPG Inc. 的 Twin Brook Capital Partners 完成了第五个直接贷款基金的募集，总资本承诺额达 39 亿美元，超过了 30 亿美元的目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/tpg-direct-lending-unit-amasses-3-9-billion-for-its-fifth-fund</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 14:01:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧元跳升至 1.10 美元，因押注美联储降息幅度可能超过欧洲央行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/euro-rises-to-seven-month-high-as-case-grows-for-fed-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于有迹象表明美国经济远弱于之前的预期，增强了对美联储降息的押注，欧元攀升至七个月来的最高水平，从而降低了美元的吸引力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/euro-rises-to-seven-month-high-as-case-grows-for-fed-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 13:11:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
