    <item>
      <title>市场押注大幅降息，全球债券市场加速上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/global-bonds-erase-this-year-s-loss-as-us-economic-outlook-sours</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球债券市场上涨，因为交易员押注美联储和其他央行将更积极地降息，因为越来越多的迹象表明经济增长放缓的速度比几周前的预期要快。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/global-bonds-erase-this-year-s-loss-as-us-economic-outlook-sours</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 01:27:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股市崩盘引发对美国国债的“疯狂抢购”：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/japanese-stocks-tumble-leading-equities-selloff-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着对全球最大经济体增长放缓的担忧加剧，全球市场高风险领域的抛售进一步加剧，股市暴跌，交易员纷纷涌向安全的债券市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/japanese-stocks-tumble-leading-equities-selloff-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 00:20:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纳斯达克 100 指数创 2022 年以来最大跌幅，抛售加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/us-stock-futures-fall</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对美国经济放缓和科技股过热上涨的担忧加剧，投资者准备迎接连续数日的波动，纳斯达克 100 指数创下近两年来最大盘中跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/us-stock-futures-fall</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 22:05:01 GMT</pubDate>
